description: General descriptive information about the deposit

label: rec_id
description: A distinct numerical identifier for the database record without further scientific significance, assigned by the data manager of mrdata.usgs.gov.

label: district
description: Name of the mining district.

label: depname
description: Most commonly used name of the deposit.

label: country
description: Country in which the deposit is located.

label: latitude
description: Geographic latitude of the deposit, in decimal degrees WGS84, south latitude negative.

label: longitude
description: Geographic longitude of the deposit, in decimal degrees WGS84, west longitude negative.

label: deptype
description: General classification of the deposit as MVT (Mississippi Valley Type), CD (clastic-dominated), or UN (unclassified)

label: alttype
description: Any alternative classification commonly given for the deposit, includes BHT (Broken Hill type), carbonate-hosted/replacement, or sh (shale) or cc (coarse clastic)

label: tectset
description: Generalized tectonic setting: PM (passive margin), BA (back arc basin), CS (continental sag), RF (rift), or UN (unclassified).

label: hostrock
description: Lithology of the host rock

label: oreton
description: Deposit size given in million metric tons of ore.

description: Tonnage of lead

label: znton
description: Tonnage of zinc

label: pbznton
description: Tonnage of lead and zinc combined

label: pbgrd

label: zngrd
description: Zinc grade

label: pbzngrd
description: Combined grade of lead and zinc

label: cugrd

label: aggrd
description: Silver grade

label: othercom
description: Other commodities present at the site

label: refprod
description: Short citations for references related to production and reserves

label: hostage
